resource.name: Hampton Small Women &  Minority Business Directory
resource.description:
The information provided is to assist with promoting contracting opportunities to small businesses within the Hampton Roads Region. The information can be searched by business type, city location and description of work.

The Directory is a resource for you and we hope you find the information helpful and of value to your business.
